{"tid":2337207,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周柏豪瞓身做藍神 杜汶澤曲線讚終於超越余文樂","createTime":"2020-12-23T06:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T06:43:49.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"799bceea1c11324cf4c9cd1a4c7baa25a16ff29c","tid":2337207,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KFw5SLwfOxNxlMC70wt8xRNpdAU=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TMIOEUP7IFH6NOEU5OAC6G5C6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKFw5SLwfOxNxlMC70wt8xRNpdAU%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTMIOEUP7IFH6NOEU5OAC6G5C6E.jpg&h=e4b14107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周柏豪一跪再跪，繼早前在社交網表態，日前更接受阿叻訪問，痛批曾和他合照的黃之鋒。<br />\n<br />\n人仔，並唔係咁賺嘅！良知，原來亦要睇情況！去年7月，周柏豪在社運期間曾呼籲市民登記做選民，結果被大陸小粉紅批鬥，更改他做「港獨豪」。其實，叫人做選民，在任何開明國家都屬於正常不過的事，可惜周柏豪一跪再跪，日前在各大社交平台貼抱女相表忠，為自己身為中國人而心存感激。當然，愛國冇問題，問題是表忠背後的動機，相信目的都只為一個_字。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：周柏豪表忠無效變「潛行雙面人」 陳百祥加持變節投藍營洗底<br />\n一不離二，周柏豪表忠行動原來還有二部曲，日前他接受阿叻訪問，痛批曾和他合照的黃之鋒和直斥去年社會運動中暴徒行私刑&hellip;&hellip;。雖然是有點姍姍來遲，但就完美示範如何瞓身投入藍營！就連杜汶澤亦忍唔住在facebook「讚」他叻仔。「我認識嘅周柏豪係叻仔嚟，好有志氣，未紅嗰陣已經好想做余文樂，跟得好貼，甚至想超越佢。今日佢終於做咗，樂仔你要加油呀！」<br />\n<br />\n傳偷食樂仔細妹兄弟反目<br />\n今年36歲的周柏豪，之所以被阿澤寸他做copycat跟貼余文樂，事關余文樂當年搞球隊並成立橫洲工業籃球隊，周柏豪與他既是兄弟又是隊友，後有指周柏豪偷食余文樂細妹，導致二人反目成仇。兄弟擘面後，有傳周柏豪更加視對方為假想敵，認為自己條件不比余文樂差，見對方在大陸撈到風生水起，為了打響知名度，決意跳入電影圈，即使他擔正的電影大部份票房不濟，但勝在片酬低，對比收400萬一部片的余文樂，30萬起跳的周柏豪任使任用，因此依然有老闆肯制。<br />\n<br />\n自創品牌成立球隊跟到貼<br />\n為了與余文樂拉近距離，當年周柏豪更有樣學樣，全方位跟足，余文樂2011年成立品牌Common Sense（CMMS），2014年再推出品牌MADNESS，周柏豪亦跟到貼，同年成立自創時裝品牌XPX。為了撼余文樂的橫洲工業，更試過自組新球隊Power Gingers（老薑）。不過，較余文樂遲7年入娛樂圈的周柏豪，即使樣樣抄到足，但至今仍未成功打入大陸市場，只可以淪為A貨。如今表忠這件事，居然成功超越余文樂，難怪連阿澤都要出post「讚」他，樂仔係時候要發力啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p3U1xb7H6SeCfKxO4qFGb51XPhk=/802x673/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U4MM2VRDIJBCNHNEA7HA6JWXGU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp3U1xb7H6SeCfKxO4qFGb51XPhk%3D%2F802x673%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU4MM2VRDIJBCNHNEA7HA6JWXGU.JPG&h=1cc54230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f443Dms2NHt8xtJil0cRwKseWoU=/802x1203/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WZCWFNZZNZD7DNXQVJ7U4HRRXQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff443Dms2NHt8xtJil0cRwKseWoU%3D%2F802x1203%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWZCWFNZZNZD7DNXQVJ7U4HRRXQ.jpg&h=caaf135b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F2OCd_HIqboIuLy44ULi5qap2Cg=/802x575/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RA47LHCCLRHIHLLW4YYNGRXKY4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF2OCd_HIqboIuLy44ULi5qap2Cg%3D%2F802x575%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRA47LHCCLRHIHLLW4YYNGRXKY4.JPG&h=1743c840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201223/WXG7HI6MCFBBLBRWVVQFCGQGPM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201223%2FWXG7HI6MCFBBLBRWVVQFCGQGPM%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp5Aoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=78f945a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201223%2FWXG7HI6MCFBBLBRWVVQFCGQGPM%2F&h=d85f4c1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201223/WXG7HI6MCFBBLBRWVVQFCGQGPM/</a>"}]}